You are designing a system to validate if a person qualifies for a membership. 
The person qualifies if their age is 21 or greater. 
Complete the condition in the following C++ code:

Consider the following C++ code:
```cpp
#include 
using namespace std;

int main() {
    int age;
    cout > age;

    if (age ___ 21) {
        cout << "You qualify for membership!" << endl;
    } else {
        cout << "You do not qualify for membership." << endl;
    }

    return 0;
}
```

